[[File:Hulsbergen_presents_DTP_at_tsinghua.jpg|thumb]]，[[北京|北京]]，就DTP原理进行演讲。]]
'''动态潮汐能'''或''' DTP'''是最新的[[潮汐能|潮汐能]]发电技术。它涉及到建立大型[[水坝|水坝]]型建筑物，从[[海岸|海岸]]一直延伸到[[海洋|海洋]]并在远端建立垂直的屏障，形成一个庞大的‘T'形。

这个T型长坝干扰与海岸平行振荡的沿大陆架海岸的潮汐波，含有强大的落差流（常见于''例如'' [[中国|中国]]，[[韩国|韩国]]和[[英国|英国]]）。<ref name=Glasgow2008>{{cite conference | title=Dynamic Tidal Power – A new approach to exploit tides | author=K. Hulsbergen, R. Steijn, G. van Banning, G. Klopman | conferenceurl=http://www.icoe2008.com/docs/programme_icoe2008.pdf | location=Brest, France | year=2008 | conference=2nd International Conference on Ocean Energy | access-date=2010-11-25 | archive-date=2012-03-14 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120314154129/http://www.icoe2008.com/docs/programme_icoe2008.pdf | dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.volkskrant.nl/archief_gratis/article782897.ece/Getijdenkracht_lift_mee_naar_Schiphol_in_zee | publisher=[[Volkskrant|Volkskrant]] | title=Getijdenkracht lift mee naar Schiphol in zee | language=nl | trans_title=Tidal power gets a free ride to Schiphol in the sea | date=28 November 1998 | author=Marieke Aarden | accessdate=2010-04-15 | archive-date=2016-02-06 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160206141135/http://www.volkskrant.nl/archief_gratis/article782897.ece/Getijdenkracht_lift_mee_naar_Schiphol_in_zee | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://archief.nrc.nl/index.php/1999/Januari/16/Overig/57/Dertig+kilometer+electriciteit | title=Dertig kilometer electriciteit | language=nl | trans_title=Thirty kilometers of electricity | publisher=[[NRC_Handelsblad|NRC Handelsblad]] | date=16 January 1999 | author=Rijkert Knoppers | accessdate=2010-04-15 | archive-date=2012-07-08 | archive-url=https://archive.today/20120708092921/http://archief.nrc.nl/index.php/1999/Januari/16/Overig/57/Dertig+kilometer+electriciteit | dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title=Meer vermogen met eb en vloed | language=nl | trans_title=More power from low and high tides | newspaper=[http://www.landwater.nl Land en Water] | author=Bas Keijts | volume=12 | year=1998 }}</ref>

这个概念是1997年由荷兰海岸工程师 Kees Hulsbergen 和 Rob Steijn 发明并获得专利的。<ref>{{cite patent|WO|9801670}}</ref>

== 描述 ==
[[File:DTP_T_dam_top-down_view.jpg|thumb]]
动态潮汐能大坝（DTP）是一种全新且尚未实践过的潮汐发电技术。工程主体是一个至少长为30公里，垂直于海岸的大坝。在大坝深入海洋的一段还可建设横坝，最终形成巨大的“T”型。DTP 大坝通过干扰海浪运动，从而在坝体的两端形成水位差，并且推动坝体内的双向涡轮机进行发电。在中国，朝鲜和英国的海岸线上，这种沿大陆架运动，而且能够产生巨大水流的潮波十分常见。
